track.name: Midnight Blues
comments: A great musician that never got his due. RIP Gary.
Gary was so much more than a guitar genius!
Love the Blues and Gary can lay it down.
Fantastic blues man. Great track. Sadly missed.
So much feelings ... through the night .... love you, Gary!!!

Gary He creates fantastic tunes that always filled with various emotions. He is looking for the identification of human emotions in different forms of performing. His unusual style of performance, somewhere on the border of blues and rock, are interested many collectors.
Great track from Mr. Moore. Wish he and Bonamassa could've played this tune together.
just the same as hendrix, this man was a amazing!
great song from a great artist......such a sad loss!
Wait a minute, there's more growlin' coming from his playing right now!! Very tasty work!!
A really fine and pure tone!! Slow and easy blues!!
